      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RUN FOREST RUN NZ (6) could only manage seventh first-up two runs ago then broke in the run and finished tailed off at the latest appearance over 1720m at Melton. Meets a similar line up so he is sure to be a force if the manners improve. MAESTRO (9) was once again right in the mix last start when runner-up over 2612m at Boort, beaten 1.5 metres. Finds a suitable assignment and will take plenty of beating once more. FROSTY GIRL NZ (10) was out of the money two starts ago then things went wrong last start when she broke and finished a distant last over 2612m at Boort. Has the talent to make her presence felt. FREMARKS PEGGY (2) was unplaced two starts ago then things went amiss last start when she broke and finished 30 metres away in fourth over 2250m at Boort. Live chance in a similar assignment.",
